<h1>Cascades and Composition </h1>
</div></div></section><section data-id="af9bd0b73c2d2b324b166702cebb2d2b"><div class="sl-block" data-block-type="text" style="width: 800px; left: 80px; top: 104px; height: auto;" data-block-id="7a06a81bfab89b51674219be99933ef1"><div class="sl-block-content" data-placeholder-tag="h2" data-placeholder-text="Title Text" style="z-index: 11;">
<h2>Lets create a component "A" with a button.</h2>
</div></div>
<div class="sl-block" data-block-type="code" style="min-width: 30px; min-height: 30px; width: 414px; height: 113px; left: 273px; top: 332px;" data-block-id="8c8076333936987e74c79b821789dbba"><div class="sl-block-content" style="z-index: 12;"><pre><code>
